(39, '2016-05-16 07:29:54', '中钢构协（空间函）［2016］第（17）号', '关于召开网格结构专业委员会二届一次全体会议暨网格结构制造高峰论坛的通知', '<p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><a name=\"OLE_LINK5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\" href=\"http://\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">为促进网格结构行业的加工制造技术、管理水平和产品质量，兹定于<span>2016</span>年<span>5</span>月在徐州市召开网格结构专业委员会二届一次全体会议及网格结构制造高峰论坛，请各位委员及相关单位届时参会。具体事宜通知如下：</span></a></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、会议时间及地点：</span></strong></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">会议时间：<span>2015</span>年<span>5</span>月<span>21</span>日全天会议，<span>22</span>日上午工厂参观</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">会议地点：徐州开元名都大酒店</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">酒店地址：江苏省徐州市泉山区湖西路<span>1</span>号</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、会议内容：</span></strong></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）网格结构专业委员会二届一次全体会议，<span>8</span>：<span>00~9</span>：<span>50</span>。主要内容有第一届委员会工作总结、第二届正副主任委员选举、明年及本届委员会工作计划等。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）网格结构制造高峰论坛，<span>10</span>：<span>00~17</span>：<span>30</span>。论坛围绕网格结构制造邀请了大会报告，并将结合议题展开讨论。主要报告有：</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 47px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）对网格结构制造业发展的若干思考（耿笑冰）；</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 47px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）网格结构制造面临工业<span>4.0</span>浪潮的思考（王瑞铮）；</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 47px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">C</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）国家天文台<span>FAST</span>项目背架加工关键技术（严永忠）；</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 47px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">D</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）螺栓球节点加工中心研制及应用（薛海滨）；</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 47px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">E</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）传统网架制造向自动化制造的迈进（钱辉）；</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 47px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">F</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）网架配件中的常见缺陷及分析（王浩）；</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 47px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">G</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）除上述报告外，还将邀请设备制造厂家的人员介绍先进制造设备。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）中国钢结构制造企业网格结构专项资质证书颁发。<span>17</span>：<span>30~18</span>：<span>00</span>（为第三次网格结构专项资质评审中获得资质的企业颁发证书）。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、工厂参观</span></strong></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">22</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日上午，针对先进加工设备及较好的网格结构生产车间进行参观。中午结束。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、住宿及交通方式：</span></strong></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">该酒店为五星级。房间价格：双床标准间：<span>380</span>元<span>/</span>间<span>/</span>天；单床豪华间：<span>498</span>元<span>/</span>间<span>/</span>天。住宿费自理。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">本次会议安排接送站，接站时间：</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">月<span>20</span>日</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：<span>00~22</span>：<span>00, 21</span>日<span>8</span>：<span>00~10</span>：<span>00</span>。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">其他时间自行前往方式：</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">A</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）徐州高铁站</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">乘坐<span>10</span>路公交到徐州站（老火车站）下，换乘<span>68</span>路公交到开元名都站下，约<span>75</span>分钟，打车约<span>50</span>分钟，约<span>60</span>元；</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">B</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）徐州火车站</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（徐州汽车总站）乘坐<span>1</span>路公交到工人医院站下，换乘<span>59</span>路公交到开元名都站下，约<span>40</span>分钟，或者徐州火车站乘<span>68</span>路公交到开元名都站下，打车约<span>20</span>分钟，约<span>25</span>元；</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">C</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）徐州观音国际机场</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">乘机场大巴（约<span>80</span>分钟，<span>20</span>元）到汉中福禧酒店，然后打车约<span>20</span>分钟，车费约<span>20</span>元，自机场直接打车，约<span>70</span>分钟，约<span>200</span>元。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、宣传资料及展览</span></strong></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">本次会议是进行单位宣传的良好机会，欢迎各会员单位采用展板或宣传资料等方式对本单位的展品进行宣传。会员单位可免费进行展览，自行携带易拉宝等展品到会场，会务组统一摆放。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、参会人员</span></strong></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">本次会议为“网格结构制造高峰论坛”，邀请了相关方面的专家，并将结合邀请报告进行讨论。请各相关企业单位的负责人、工厂生产负责人及质量管理人员参会，互相取长补短、共同提高。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">本次会议不收取会务费，每单位参会人员以不超过<span>3</span>人为宜。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">为了更好地召开本次论坛，促进行业制造水平，请网格结构专业委员会委员及各会员单位将本通知转发给网格结构相关单位。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请将<a name=\"OLE_LINK10\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"OLE_LINK9\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\" href=\"http://\">会议回执</a>（见附件）于<span>5</span>月<span>15</span>日前返回秘书处，以便确认宾馆住房和安排接站。</span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">空间结构分会秘书处联系方式：</span></strong></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">地址：北京市朝阳区平乐园<span>100</span>号（邮编：<span>100124</span>）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height: 27px;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">电话（传真）：<span>010-67391496&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13px;white-space: normal;line-height