\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">王泽强 &nbsp;&nbsp;王德勤 &nbsp;&nbsp;朱万旭 &nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">任俊超 &nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">刘 &nbsp;健</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">刘中华 &nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">刘红波 &nbsp;&nbsp;孙文波 &nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">李海旺</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;吴金志 &nbsp;&nbsp;沈雁彬 &nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">张 &nbsp;琳 &nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">罗 &nbsp;斌 &nbsp;&nbsp;周 &nbsp;岱 &nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">周 &nbsp;健</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">周黎光 </span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;高继领</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;黄 &nbsp;颖 &nbsp;&nbsp;曹正罡</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;梁存之 &nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">葛家琪</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">组织委员会名单（按姓氏笔画排序）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">主任委员</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">吴金志</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">副主任委员</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">于吉圣 &nbsp;&nbsp;马维展 &nbsp;&nbsp;张可文 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">罗</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">斌</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">委 &nbsp;员</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">王成林 &nbsp;&nbsp;王海兵&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;刘占省&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;阮杨捷 &nbsp;孙国军&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;李雄彦&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;许立准&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;朱明亮 &nbsp;&nbsp;余玉洁&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;沈宇洲 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">张秀华&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;张佳璐 &nbsp;&nbsp;郑向红 &nbsp;&nbsp;周 &nbsp;巍&nbsp;&nbsp;郭丽艳 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">高娅静</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;黄 &nbsp;海</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:35px;line-height:29px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">近几年，我国索结构体系越来越丰富，索结构技术不断创新发展，已建成多项同类结构世界最大工程。可以说，索结构已经成为大跨度、大空间建筑的主角，这些工程设计与施工紧密衔接，建造技术</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">十分</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">复杂，充分展示了我国工程技术人员的聪明才智。为进一步提高我国索结构科研、设计、施工及生产的技术水平，促进行业健康发展，</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">“</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">第三届全国索结构技术交流会</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">”</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">将于<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span>12-14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span></span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">在苏州市隆重召开，旨在总结交流已建、在建重大索结构工程的建设经验，研究索结构工程中热点、难点问题，探讨行业发展方向，并组织参观苏州工业园区体育中心游泳馆和体育场工程</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">（游泳馆采用马鞍形单层索网结构，跨度<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">107m</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">；</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">体育场轮辐式单层索网，跨度长轴约<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">260m</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，短轴约</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">230m</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）</span></span></strong><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:35px;line-height:29px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">一、会议内容</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:14px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）索结构工程的新构思、新方案。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:14px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）邀请国内重大工程项目的负责人介绍索结构工程创新情况。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:14px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）总结交流已建、在建重大索结构工程的建设经验。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:14px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）针对索结构工程中的热点、难点问题，进行深入探讨。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:14px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）组织参观苏州工业园区体育中心游泳馆和体育场</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">。</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">二、主题报告</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">（不分排名）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&gt;</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">题目待定</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">董石麟（中国工程院院士）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&gt;</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">题目待定</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">汪大绥（华东建筑设计研究总院顾问总工程师，全国工程勘察设计大师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;题目待定</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">傅学怡（深圳大学教授，全国工程勘察设计大师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;拉索特性及张弦结构研究进展与工程实践</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:19px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">陈志华</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">（</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">天津大学教授）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;非对称开口式整体张拉索膜结构技术研究</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">葛家琪</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">（</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">中国航空规划设计研究总院有限公司首席专家，总结构师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;500m口径球面射电望远镜索网结构设计研究</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">朱忠义</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">（</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">北京市建筑设计院有限公司副总工程师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;具有劲性索受力特点的单层铝合金网格结构——上海南大门屋盖设计</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">周 &nbsp;健（华东建筑设计院有限公司副总工程师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;苏州工业园区体育中心结构设计</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">徐晓明（上海建筑设计院有限公司总工程师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;苏州工业园区体育中心索网结构关键施工技术</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">罗 &nbsp;斌（东南大学教授）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;超大跨马鞍形索穹顶结构施工关键技术</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">周黎光（北京市建筑工程研究院有限责任公司结构工程研究所所长）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;镇江长江大桥主缆施工技术（</span><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">世界上荷载最重、设计时速最快的公铁两用悬索桥，主跨1092m</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:19px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">汪芳进（中铁大桥局工程管理部总工程师</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">，</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">连镇铁路镇江长江大桥项目部副经理）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;空间单索面曲梁悬索人行景观桥施工关键技术 </span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">伍小平（上海建工集团工程研究总院技术总监兼施工控制研究所所长，教授级高工）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;大跨度体育馆单层索网钢结构施工技术</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">王海兵（中建钢构有限公司项目总工程师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;密封钢丝绳-应用广泛的多功能产品</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Martin Bechtold<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（瑞士布鲁克法策钢丝绳公司结构钢丝绳事业部经理，工学博士）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;单索结构点支式玻璃幕墙设计与施工常见问题解析</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">王德勤（北京德宏幕墙技术科研中心主任，教授级高级工程师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px\">三、</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">会议时间地点</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">会议地点：苏州</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">会议时间：<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下午报到，召开索结构专业委员会二届三次工作会议；</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日全天大会技术交流；</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上午参观，下午离会。 </span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">四</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">、论文征集</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）会议论文集将以《施工技术》</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年增刊的形式公开出版，有主管部门批准的正式刊号。论文要求具有原创性，有独到见解和学术价值，应反映近期应用与研究成果，不接受已公开发表过的论文。稿件经学术委员会评审后择优录用，论文一经录用将及时通知作者。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:19px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）截止日期：</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日前提交全文。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:19px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）投稿邮箱：</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">gaoyj@cadg.cn</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">，</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">weiz@cadg.cn<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，提交论文时请注明</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">索结构会议投稿</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。论文格式请参照近期《施工技术》杂志，并提供作者简介（工作单位、职务、职称、手机、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">E-mail</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、通讯地址、邮编）。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:19px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）评选优秀论文：聘请业内专家从入编的论文中评选出优秀论文，设一、二、三等奖</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个奖项，获奖论文作者将获得由主办单位颁发的证书</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">及相关奖励</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">五</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">、会议招商</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">本届索结构大会提供协办单位、会场展位、论文集广告等多种宣传形式，因名额有限，有需要的企业请及时与会务组联系。</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">六</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">、费</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">用</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）会务费：</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人；</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">空间</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">结构分会会员单位<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:54px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">收款单位：亚太建设