(49, '2016-05-25 06:57:53', '中钢构协（空间函）[2016] 第（26）号', '关于组织天津理工大学体育馆索穹顶结构现场观摩会的通知', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-family: &#39;Songti SC&#39;;\">各位常务理事、索结构专业委员会委员：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-family: &#39;Songti SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></span>中国钢结构协会空间结构分会索结构专业委员会和天津市钢结构学会拟于<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">6</span>月<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">3</span>日<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">-4</span>日联合组织天津理工大学体育馆索穹顶现场观摩活动。天津理工大学体育馆索穹顶目前为我国第一个跨度百米级的索穹顶结构工程，目前索穹顶的拉索大部分已张拉就位。会议内容通知如下：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; font-family: &#39;Songti SC&#39;;\"><strong>一、会议日程</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"></span>2016</span><font face=\"Songti SC\">年</font><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">6</span><font face=\"Songti SC\">月</font><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">3</span><font face=\"Songti SC\">日&nbsp;</font><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">09:00-18:00 </span><font face=\"Songti SC\">报到地点：天津赛象酒店（西青区华苑产业区梅苑路</font><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">8</span><font face=\"Songti SC\">号）</font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18:30-21:00 </span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Songti SC&#39;;\">欢迎晚宴</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"></span>2016<span style=\"font-family: &#39;Songti SC&#39;;\">年</span>6<span style=\"font-family: &#39;Songti SC&#39;;\">月</span>4</span><font face=\"Songti SC\">日&nbsp;</font><font face=\"Helvetica\">08:30-10:00 </font><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Songti SC&#39;;\">领导发言及相关技术报告</span></p><p style=\