px;\">周黎光 </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;高继领</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;黄 &nbsp; 颖 &nbsp;&nbsp;曹正罡</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;梁存之 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 14px;\">葛家琪</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">组织</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">委员会名单（按姓氏笔</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">画</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">排序）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">主任委员</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">吴金志</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">副主任委员</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">丁勇祥</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;陈 &nbsp;韬 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">马维展 &nbsp;&nbsp;张可文 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">罗</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">斌</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">委 &nbsp;员</span></p><p style=\"line-height:20px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">于吉圣</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">王成林 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">王海兵 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">刘占省 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">阮杨捷 &nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">孙国军 &nbsp;&nbsp;李雄彦 &nbsp;&nbsp;许立准 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">朱明亮 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">余玉洁 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">沈宇洲 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">张秀华 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">张佳璐 &nbsp;&nbsp;张晓冰 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">郑向红 &nbsp;周 &nbsp;巍 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">郭丽艳 </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 14px;\">高娅静</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;黄 &nbsp;海 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">程大勇</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:35px;line-height:29px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:35px;line-height:29px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">近几年，我国索结构体系越来越丰富，索结构技术不断创新发展，已建成多项同类结构世界最大工程。可以说，索结构已经成为大跨度、大空间建筑的主角，这些工程设计与施工紧密衔接，建造技术</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">十分</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">复杂，充分展示了我国工程技术人员的聪明才智。为进一步提高我国索结构科研、设计、施工及生产的技术水平，促进行业健康发展，</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">“</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">第三届全国索结构技术交流会</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">”</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">将于<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">12~14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span></span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">在苏州市隆重召开，旨在总结交流已建、在建重大索结构工程的建设经验，研究索结构工程中热点、难点问题，探讨行业发展方向，并组织参观苏州工业园区体育中心游泳馆和体育场工程（游泳馆采用马鞍形单层索网结构，跨度<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">107m</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">；</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">体育场轮辐式单层索网，跨度长轴约<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">260m</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，短轴约</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">230m</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">一、会议日程</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">8月12日 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">全天</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">报到；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">8月13日 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">技术交流会</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">-</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">会议主题报告；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">8月14日 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">参观苏州工业园区体育中心游泳馆和体育场工程</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">二</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">、主题报告</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14px;\">题目待定</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">董石麟（中国工程院院士）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14px;\">题目待定</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 21px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">沈世钊（中国工程院院士）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&gt;</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">题目待定</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">汪大绥（华东建筑设计研究总院顾问总工程师，全国工程勘察设计大师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">题目待定</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">傅学怡（深圳大学教授，全国工程勘察设计大师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">拉索特性及张弦结构研究进展与工程实践</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:19px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">陈志华</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">（</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">天津大学教授）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;非对称开口式整体张拉索膜结构技术研究</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">葛家琪</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">（</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">中国航空规划设计研究总院有限公司首席专家，总结构师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;500m口径球面射电望远镜索网结构设计研究</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">朱忠义</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">（</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">北京市建筑设计院有限公司副总工程师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;具有劲性索受力特点的单层铝合金网格结构——上海南大门屋盖设计</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">周 &nbsp;健（华东建筑设计院有限公司副总工程师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;苏州工业园区体育中心结构设计</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">徐晓明（上海建筑设计院有限公司结构二所所长）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;苏州工业园区体育中心索网结构关键施工技术</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">罗 &nbsp;斌（东南大学教授）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;超大跨马鞍形索穹顶结构施工关键技术</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">周黎光（北京市建筑工程研究院有限责任公司结构工程研究所所长）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;镇江长江大桥主缆施工技术（</span><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">世界上荷载最重、设计时速最快的公铁两用悬索桥，主跨1092m</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:19px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">汪芳进（中铁大桥局工程管理部总工程师</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">，</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">连镇铁路镇江长江大桥项目部副经理）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;空间单索面曲梁悬索人行景观桥施工关键技术 </span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">伍小平（上海建工集团工程研究总院技术总监兼施工控制研究所所长，教授级高工）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">苏州工业园区体育中心项目工程建设情况介绍</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;程大勇 （中建三局苏州工业园区体育中心项目总工程师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;大跨度体育馆单层索网钢结构施工技术</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">王海兵（中建钢构有限公司项目总工程师）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">密封钢丝绳-应用广泛的多功能产品</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Martin Bechtold<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（瑞士布鲁克法策钢丝绳公司结构钢丝绳事业部经理，工学博士）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;单索结构点支式玻璃幕墙设计与施工常见问题解析</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">王德勤（北京德宏幕墙技术科研中心主任，教授级高级工程师</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">&gt;</span><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">索结构产品创新技术在国内外工程中应用</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;杜学国 （</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">巨力索具股份有限公司</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\">报告顺序与题目以会议现场安排为准</span></p><p style=\"line-height:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">三</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">、会议招商</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">本届索结构大会提供协办单位、会场展位、论文集广告等多种宣传形式，因名额有限，有需要的企业请及时与会务组联系。</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">四</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">、费</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">用</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）会务费：</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人；</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">空间</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">结构分会会员单位<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:54px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:12px\">收款单位：亚太建设科技信息研究院有限公司 &nbsp;&nbsp;开户银行：招商银行北京东三环支行</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;text-indent:54px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:12px\">账号：<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">110908001310606 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汇款用途：</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\">索结构</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:12px\">会务费（请务必注明）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">（<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）会议期间，食宿统一安排，住宿费用自理。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">五、时间、地点</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">报到时间</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">：<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2016 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">8 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">12 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日（星期五） &nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">会议地点：</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">苏州白金汉爵大酒店</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;地址：江苏省苏州市相城区相城大道<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1111</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号</span></span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\">。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:14px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\">酒店电话： <span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">(0512)66837666</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 18px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 12px\">&nbsp;交通路线</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\">乘火车：1）苏州站，乘出租车到苏州白金汉爵酒店约10分钟，费用15元左右；2）苏州北站，乘出租车到苏州白金汉爵酒店约15分钟，费用约20元左右。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\">乘飞机：1）至无锡硕放机场，然后乘出租车大概30分钟到苏州；2）至上海虹桥机场，乘地铁坐一站，然后到虹桥火车站再换乘高铁，大概1小时到苏州。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:19px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">六</span></strong><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">、</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 14px\">联系方式</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left: 28px;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:14px\">空间结构分会秘书处联系方式：</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 28px;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">地 &nbsp;址：北京市朝阳区平乐园<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号（邮编：</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">100124</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 28px;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">电 &nbsp;话（传真）：<sp