(54, '2016-07-19 05:01:22', '中钢构协（空间函）［2016］第（36）号', '关于召开索结构专业委员会二届三次全体会议的通知', '<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:125%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">索结构专业委员会二届三次全体会议将于2016年8月12日在苏州召开，会议涉及多项索结构行业发展的议题需要研讨与共商，敬请各位委员提前安排好时间，拨冗出席，</span><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">并将参会信息于</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">7</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">月</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">31</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">日前反馈给秘书处或微信</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">孙国军</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:125%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">本次会议相关情况通知如下</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;line-height: 125%;font-size: 14px\">：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:125%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 16px\">一、会议内容</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:125%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">讨论索结构专业委员会委员资格事宜；</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;