(75, '2017-05-05 15:48:46', '', '关于召开空间结构分会2017年年会的通知（第3号）', '<p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">兹定于</span>2017<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span>6<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">月</span><span style=\"border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-style: dashed;border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204)\">10-12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日在上海地区召开两年一度的空间结构分会</span>2017<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年年会。本次大会是在国家大力倡导建筑工业化及信息化的大背景下召开的，将对空间结构领域的科研、设计、制作、安装以及管理等方面的发展及最新成果进行广泛深入的交流。期间将召开常务理事会、三个专业委员会以及成立专家委员会等工作会议，并颁发第十届空间结构奖的证书和奖杯。望全体会员单位和从事空间结构行业的相关单位届时派代表参会。现将具体事宜通知如下：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;margin-top: 10px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>1</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、会议时间及日程：</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）会议时间：</span>2017<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span>6<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">月</span><span style=\"border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-style: dashed;border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204)\">10-12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日。</span>9<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日</span>9:00~22:00<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">报到</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）会议日程：</span>9<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日下午及晚上工作会议；</span>10<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、</span>11<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日技术交流；</span>12<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日上午工程参观。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 49px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">10<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日上午：大会开幕式、大会特邀报告；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 49px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">10<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日下午：大会特邀报告</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 49px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">11<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日上午：膜结构、网格结构和索结构三个分会场技术交流；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 49px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">11<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日下午：大会特邀报告、第十届空间结构奖颁奖、闭幕式。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 49px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">12<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日上午：技术参观，午餐后大会结束。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;margin-top: 10px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>2</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、工作会议内容：</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）</span>9<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日下午，</span>14:30-18:00<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，网格结构、膜结构和索结构三个专业委员会分别召开委员会全体会议；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）</span>9<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日晚上，</span>19:30-22:00<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，六届三次常务理事会议。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）</span>11<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日下午，第十届空间结构奖颁奖。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;margin-top: 10px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>3</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、技术交流内容：</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>1</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）大会主题</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：<strong>面向建筑工业化与信息化的空间结构</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>2</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）交流内容</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：包括空间结构所涉及的网格结构、索结构和膜结构等的科研、设计、制作、安装以及管理等方面的工业化与信息化的发展及最新实践。包括但不限于下列内容：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;margin-left: 24px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">A<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）空间结构中各种节点的发展及工程实践、新型节点的研发、分析、试验、设计、加工及工程应用；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">B<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）空间结构设计、施工、制作中的新技术，</span>BIM<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">技术的应用与实践；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">C<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）空间结构新体系及其它新技术、新产品。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>3</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）会议交流方式</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：会议将采取专家作大会特邀报告和小组交流（膜结构、网格结构、索结构）的方式进行。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>4</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）大会特邀报告</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span>1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）空间结构工业化道路探索</span>-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">沿革、经验与前途（蓝天</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">空间结构分会名誉理事长）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span>2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）</span>500<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">米口径射电望远镜主动反射面结构体系创新回顾</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 56px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（沈世钊</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">哈尔滨工业大学教授</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中国工程院院士）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0