 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span>11<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）索具锚具的现代化制造（杜学国</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">巨力索具股份有限公司副总裁）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span>12<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）结构创造建筑之美</span>——<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">丽水市体育馆结构形态设计（姚亚雄</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">华东建筑集团股份有限公司设计中心技术总监</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">总建筑师）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;margin-top: 10px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>4</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、论文征集及发言稿征集</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">本次大会将广泛征集相关论文，并编辑印刷论文集。欢迎投稿，投稿者需将全文（或会议交流发言稿</span>PPT<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）于</span>2017<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span>5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">月</span>25<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日前发邮件至分会秘书处，其中需注明作者的详细联系方式。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 23px;color: rg